    body {background-color: #B0E2FF;
        font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    };
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2 style="font-size:300%; margin-left: 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #000000;">Scott Stadum's CV Bot</h2>
    <p style="font-size:200%; margin-left: 20px;"> Welcome to Scott Stadum's CV Bot.  Feel free to ask it anything about Scott, from his education to work history to his hobbies.  He's a complex character and there's plenty to learn about Scott!</p>
<p style="margin-left: 20px;">Use these commands to get started:</p>
<ul>
<li><mark>Hello</mark> - to start the conversation</li>
<li><mark>CV</mark> - to download a copy of Scott's CV</li>
<li><mark>Linkedin</mark> - to see Scott's LinkedIn profile</li>
<li><mark>Art</mark> - to see Scott's digital art</li>
<li><mark>Writing</mark> - see Scott's writing examples</li>
<li><mark>Blog</mark> - see Scott's blog</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin-left: 20px;">You can also ask questions like:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Tell me about yourself</li>
    <li>Where are you from?</li>
    <li>What are your goals?</li>
    <li>What are your salary expectations?</li>
</ul>
</ul>
</body>
</html>
